Package nl.codevs.strinput.system

Class StrCenter

java.lang.Object
nl.codevs.strinput.system.StrCenter
Direct Known Subclasses:
DiscordCenter, SpigotCenter
public class StrCenter extends Object
Input center. The main class for interacting with Strinput.
Make sure to point command calls to onCommand(List, StrUser)
Since:
v0.1
See Also:
nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc
